TextEng: How do you know my name?
How you know me name?
That's right. I'm <FullName>. Who are you?
That right. Me <FullName>. Who you be?
My name is none of your business.
Text: 제 이름은 당신이 알 바가 아닙니다.

TextEng: Me name not be you business.
Text: 내 이름 네가 알 일 아니야.

TextEng: I think you have me confused with someone else.
Text: 저를 다른 사람과 혼동하신 것 같은데요.

TextEng: Me think you got me mixed up with some other person.
Text: 나 생각엔 너 나를 다른 사람이랑 헷갈린 것 같아.

TextEng: Enough with the flattery. I've got work to do.
You're not so bad yourself, Delvar.
Me not got time for flattery.
You not so bad youself, Delvar.
Why did Gend tell you to keep an eye out for me?
Why Gend want you to watch for me?
I'll be going now.
Me go now.
I don't have time for your childish insults.
Me not got time for you insults.
Watch your mouth or I'll smash your pretty-boy face into a bloody pulp.
Text: 입 조심하는 게 좋을 걸요, 안 그러면 그 예쁜 얼굴을 피투성이로 만들어 버릴 테니까.

TextEng: You take that back or me smash you pretty-boy face to pieces!
Text: 말 취소해 아니면 나 네 예쁜 얼굴 박살 내!

TextEng: Have you found anything out about the Words of Power?
Text: 권능의 언령에 대해 뭔가 알아낸 게 있나요?

TextEng: You know stuff 'bout Power Words?
What's the information?
What information?
Tell me about the orc bandits.
Tell me about the magical portal.
I want to ask you something else.
You tell 'bout orc bandits.
You tell 'bout magic portal.
Me want ask other stuff.
Anything else?
You didn't go through the portal?
You not go through portal?
Where can I find this portal?
Text: 그 차원문은 어디서 찾을 수 있죠?

TextEng: Where me find this portal?
What do you plan to do now?
What you gonna do now?
Maybe you could help me in my mission.
Text: 제 임무를 도와주실 수 있을 것 같은데요.

TextEng: Maybe you help me in me mission.
Text: 내 임무 도와줄 수 있을 것 같아.

TextEng: Who are you again?
Who you be again?
Sure, go over the information again.
Sure. You tell me info again.
Looks like you're all alone out here. You better give me fifty gold. For protection.
Text: 여기 혼자 있는 것 같은데. 금화 50개 주는 게 좋을 거예요. 보호비로요.

TextEng: You all by youself here. You give me fifty gold and me protect you.
Text: 여기 혼자 있네. 금화 50개 줘 그럼 나 보호해줄게.

TextEng: Bandits. Wild creatures. Me. You wouldn't want to end up a corpse in the ditch, after all.
Text: 노상강도들. 야생 생명체들. 저. 결국 도랑에서 시체로 발견되고 싶진 않을 테니까요.

TextEng: No one, I guess. You can probably look after yourself. Forget I said anything.
Text: 아무도 없겠죠. 혼자 조심하면 될 것 같네요. 제가 한 말은 잊으세요.

TextEng: Bandits. Monsters. Me. You not want end up dead in the ditch, right?
Text: 노상강도. 괴물. 나. 도랑에서 죽은 채로 발견되고 싶지 않지?

TextEng: Me guess you can look after youself. Nevermind.
Text: 나 생각엔 혼자 조심하면 될 것 같아. 신경 쓰지 마.

TextEng: Gend finds out, you die.
